  "outer_html": "<article class=\"fightingground_page__fightingground__image__modal__Mcrk3 modal\"><div class=\"fightingground_modal__bg__XSMNL\"></div><section><div><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"><img alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20version=%271.1%27%20width=%271920%27%20height=%271080%27/%3e\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></span><img alt=\"\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"intrinsic\" style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: none; margin: auto; display: block; width: 0px; height: 0px; min-width: 100%; max-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"><noscript></noscript></span></div><div class=\"fightingground_disp__SKPmW\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"><img alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20version=%271.1%27%20width=%271600%27%20height=%27919%27/%3e\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></span><img alt=\"\" src=\"/6/assets/images/mode/fg/game_screen.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"intrinsic\" style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: none; margin: auto; display: block; width: 0px; height: 0px; min-width: 100%; max-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"><noscript></noscript></span><ul class=\"fightingground_modal__drive__list__z2Ti_\"><li class=\"fightingground_num_01__FA04p\"><h4>体力ゲージ</h4><p>操作キャラクターの残体力を表すゲージ。</p></li><li class=\"fightingground_num_02__XkYrs\"><h4>ドライブゲージ</h4><p>ゲージをドライブシステムに使用する。\r\nゲージが0になると”バーンアウト”状態になり、回復するまでドライブシステムを利用する技は一時的に使用できなくなる。</p></li><li class=\"fightingground_num_03__MqNxt\"><h4>タイムカウンター</h4><p>1ラウンド中の残り時間を表示。</p></li><li class=\"fightingground_num_04__VsZNM\"><h4>ラウンドアイコン</h4><p>バトルのラウンド進行度を表すアイコン。ラウンドに勝利すると1つ点灯する。</p></li><li class=\"fightingground_num_05__YG_cg\"><h4>キャラクターアイコン</h4><p>操作キャラクターの名前と顔アイコン。</p></li><li class=\"fightingground_num_06__blnzF\"><h4>スーパーアーツゲージ</h4><p>ゲージを消費して強力なスーパーアーツを使用できる。\r\n技をヒットさせると増加し、ゲージは最大3ストックまで溜められる。ラウンドで使用しなかったゲージは、次のラウンドに持ち越しができる。</p></li></ul></div><div><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"><img alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20version=%271.1%27%20width=%271920%27%20height=%271080%27/%3e\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></span><img alt=\"\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"intrinsic\" style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: none; margin: auto; display: block; width: 0px; height: 0px; min-width: 100%; max-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"><noscript></noscript></span></div><p class=\"close\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"><img alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20version=%271.1%27%20width=%2765%27%20height=%2767%27/%3e\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; width: initial; height: initial; background: none; opacity: 1; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></span><img alt=\"\" src=\"/6/assets/images/common/close_interface.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"intrinsic\" style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: none; margin: auto; display: block; width: 0px; height: 0px; min-width: 100%; max-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"><noscript></noscript></span></p></section></article>",
